    "textRight": ">不，我最喜欢你了。",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101505/vo_full_101505-5-40",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101505/vo_full_101505-5-39"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 820100,
      "motion": 300
     }
    ],
    "textRight": ">你教会了我很多事情。",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101505/vo_full_101505-5-41",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101505/vo_full_101505-5-40"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 820100,
      "motion": 100
     }
    ],
    "textRight": ">最重要的是@>你让我懂得了什么是温柔。",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101505/vo_full_101505-5-42",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101505/vo_full_101505-5-41"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 820100,
      "motion": 200
     }
    ],
    "textRight": ">所以我最喜欢你了。",
    "voiceFull": "fullvoice/section_101505/vo_full_101505-5-43",
    "voiceFullStop": "fullvoice/section_101505/vo_full_101505-5-42"
   },
   {
    "chara": [
     {
      "id": 820100,
      "motion": 300
     }
    ],
    "textRight": ">但正因如此，@>我才想放你自由。",
